						<li>configure the Vagrant file with your own information</li>
						<ul><li>If you are not sure where to get the ORGANIZATION, OR USERNAME, either look into ~/.chef/knife or <a href="https://manage.opscode.com/organizations">Opscode Managment</a></li></ul>
						<li>append: "export EDITOR=mate" to your ~/.profile</li>
						<ul><li>If you don't have textmate you can add vim, vi, sublim, or any other editor</li></ul>						
						<li>Run: knife node create mv-develop</li>
